FBIS3-34999 "drnes033_n_94002" FBIS-NES-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Feb 1994 LEBANON Buwayz Denies Israeli Threats Received Via U.S. NC1602193894 Beirut Voice of Lebanon in Arabic 1715 GMT 16 Feb 94 NC1602193894 Beirut Voice of Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Foreign Minister Fariz Buwayz had denied that U.S. Secretary of State Warren Christopher's message has included any Israeli threats. He told REUTER that the escalation of violence in the south is the result of the Israeli occupation. He said that achieving quick progress in the peace talks toward recognition of the principle of withdrawal from the south is needed to calm the situation.
